WEBVTT

00:00.536 --> 00:03.163
Let's learn the names for appliances.

00:08.006 --> 00:09.885
This is a stove.

00:15.475 --> 00:17.865
The pizza is in the oven.

00:22.301 --> 00:24.040
He used the microwave.

00:32.701 --> 00:34.707
He likes his rice cooker.

00:40.634 --> 00:42.070
This is a toaster.

00:49.386 --> 00:50.926
Do you have a toaster oven?

00:56.607 --> 00:58.555
We use our coffeemaker in the morning.

01:04.215 --> 01:06.042
Be careful! The kettle is hot.

01:13.631 --> 01:15.667
The dog is in the fridge.

01:24.270 --> 01:26.344
The cat opened the freezer.

01:38.808 --> 01:40.603
This is a washing machine.

01:47.179 --> 01:49.290
The cat is in the dryer.

01:55.055 --> 01:57.056
This is a hairdryer.

